					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">What I do for a quick debugger check, is put something like this right before where I want to check:
<br />stop: jmp stop
<br />
<br />Then in a debugger, usually FCEU you can hit the step button, then you can step through it from there.
<br />
<br />Usually the NSF is assembled separately (with whatever assembler), though you could include the driver source (it usually wouldn't matter).
<br />
<br />It's most common to put the music starting at $8000, and you'll have to place any DPCM samples separately (at $C000 or above).</div>

